
lagte ho dil ke sachche lagte ho
meri yahi tamanna hai
ki main tumase pyar karu tumse ikaraar karu
tum mujhe achche lagte ho dil ke sachche lagte ho
meri yahi tamanna hai
ki main tumaspyar karu tumse ikaraar karu
dekhati hoon jab main tumko dhadkane kuchh bolti hai
tum ho naadaan tum kya jaano raaz kya kya kholti hai
suno suno zidd naa karo yu naa sanam aahen bharo
main pyasi tanhai mein kab tak intezaar karu, main tumse pyar karu
tum mujhe achchi lagti ho dil ki sachchi lagati ho
meri yahi tamanna hai
ki main tumse pyar karu tumse ikaraar karu
mere dilbar iss adaa pe ho raha hai dil deewana
badh rahi hai bekaraari hai sama bhi ashiqana
dard-de-jigar mujhako diya tumne mera chain liya
aaon aise aalam mein tumhen main bekaraar karu, main tumse pyar karu
tum mujhe achche lagte ho dil ke sachche lagte ho
meri yahi tamanna hai
ki main tumse pyar karu tumse ikaraar karu